      <title>希捷預計第四季利潤將因雲端客戶的成長而增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/seagate-forecasts-higher-q4-profit-boost-cloud-customers-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由於雲端客戶對其記憶體晶片的需求增加，希捷科技公司週二預測第四季獲利將高於華爾街預期，最近一個季度的獲利預期超出預期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/seagate-forecasts-higher-q4-profit-boost-cloud-customers-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 20:46:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於類比晶片需求改善，TI 預測季度收入高於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/analog-chipmaker-texas-instruments-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德州儀器 (TI) 週二預測第二季營收將高於華爾街預期，顯示對其模擬半導體的需求上升，導致該晶片製造商的股價在盤後交易中上漲 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/analog-chipmaker-texas-instruments-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 20:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
