      <title>ASMI上調第二季營收預期，中國訂單強於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-q2-revenue-forecast-chinese-bookings-stronger-than-expected-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[晶圓加工設備供應商 ASM International (ASMI) 週二上調了今年第二季度的收入預期，理由是中國需求強於預期以及先進邏輯和記憶體的銷售額增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-q2-revenue-forecast-chinese-bookings-stronger-than-expected-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 16:50:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
